            "steam_appid": 881060,
            "required_age": 0,
            "is_free": false,
            "detailed_description": "<strong>Fortune &amp; Gloria</strong> is an action platformer where you save the day in procedurally generated missions!<br><br>Grab your trusty assault rifle, a handful of grenades, and join Nate &quot;Fortune&quot; Cobb and Gloria Guerrero on a mission to rescue hostages, take out the bad guys and blow stuff up!<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/881060/extras/3_scenes_loop.jpg?t=1542908325\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Co-Op Missions! Grab a friend or have an AI ally follow you into action!<br></li><li>Solo Missions! Go it alone for extra challenge and test your mettle!<br></li><li>Unlimited mission levels through procedural generation<br></li><li>Multiple environment including desert, snow, urban, and more<br></li><li>Fight multiple enemy groups like gangs, gun runners and terrorists<br></li><li>Shoot down enemy helicopters and blow up enemy tanks<br></li><li>Blast your way through the terrain to find your own path</li></ul><br>Get ready to be dropped off in the hot zone and try to rescue as many hostages as you can, while taking out any enemies you encounter, before beating the boss and getting on the chopper heading off to the next mission.",
            "about_the_game": "<strong>Fortune &amp; Gloria</strong> is an action platformer where you save the day in procedurally generated missions!<br><br>Grab your trusty assault rifle, a handful of grenades, and join Nate &quot;Fortune&quot; Cobb and Gloria Guerrero on a mission to rescue hostages, take out the bad guys and blow stuff up!<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/881060/extras/3_scenes_loop.jpg?t=1542908325\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Co-Op Missions! Grab a friend or have an AI ally follow you into action!<br></li><li>Solo Missions! Go it alone for extra challenge and test your mettle!<br></li><li>Unlimited mission levels through procedural generation<br></li><li>Multiple environment including desert, snow, urban, and more<br></li><li>Fight multiple enemy groups like gangs, gun runners and terrorists<br></li><li>Shoot down enemy helicopters and blow up enemy tanks<br></li><li>Blast your way through the terrain to find your own path</li></ul><br>Get ready to be dropped off in the hot zone and try to rescue as many hostages as you can, while taking out any enemies you encounter, before beating the boss and getting on the chopper heading off to the next mission.",
            "short_description": "Fortune &amp; Gloria is an action platformer where you save the day in procedurally generated missions! Grab your trusty assault rifle, a handful of grenades, and join Nate &quot;Fortune&quot; Cobb and Gloria Guerrero on a mission to rescue hostages, take out the bad guys and blow stuff up!",
